                "description": "Simulate Xendit Invoice berhasil dibayar di sandbox — **satu klik, tanpa buka browser**.\n\nXendit akan kirim webhook `status: PAID` ke callback URL → Laravel set payment `paid`.\n\n**Setup (sekali saja):**\n1. Isi `xendit_secret_key` di collection variables\n2. Set Webhook URL di [Xendit Dashboard](https://dashboard.xendit.co) → Settings → Webhooks → Invoice paid → `https://your-ngrok.io/api/webhooks/xendit`\n3. Aktifkan Xendit → Settings → Webhooks → toggle Invoice paid ✅\n\n**Flow per test:**\n1. `POST /api/payments/initiate` dengan `gateway: xendit` → `invoice_id` tersimpan otomatis\n2. Send request ini → Xendit trigger webhook\n3. `GET /api/payments/{{payment_id}}/status` → status harus `paid`\n\n⚠️ **Sandbox only**"
